room_title: Escape room "The Captain" by beat60 in Gadsden
room_description:
You and your team have just committed one of the largest bank robberies in American history. However, Captain Thatcher has surveillance footage of the robbery on his computer! That footage will put you all in jail for at least 40 years.
Captain Thatcher is currently out of town following up on a lead. However, he will be returning in an hour so you've got to sneak into his office and delete the footage before he returns.
